videos.description: Quentin Goodin shows his strength in the paint, rejecting UConn early in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Xavier's Goodin comes up with big block) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Xavier's Goodin comes up with big block

videos.description: Alterique Gilbert drives to the hoop and tosses it back to James Bouknight for a jam vs. Xavier.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gilbert drops it off to Bouknight for UConn slam) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Gilbert drops it off to Bouknight for UConn slam

videos.description: Josh Carlton's second effort tips the ball in for UConn, as the Huskies try to overcome a 10-point halftime deficit in the second half vs. Xavier.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Carlton sticks with it for UConn and tips it in) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Carlton sticks with it for UConn and tips it in

videos.description: Zach Freemantle rejects UConn at one end, picks up the rebound and hits a clutch layup at the other as the Musketeers stay close to the Huskies.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Freemantle blocks and hits layup for Xavier) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Freemantle blocks and hits layup for Xavier

videos.description: Tyler Polley drains a clutch 3-pointer in the final minutes of the second half to help the Huskies pull away vs. Xavier.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Polley hits sweet off-balance 3 for UConn) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Polley hits sweet off-balance 3 for UConn

videos.description: Naji Marshall pulls up from near the logo and hits a deep 3-pointer to tie UConn at 56-56 and eventually force overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Marshall's deep 3 pulls Xavier even with UConn) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Marshall's deep 3 pulls Xavier even with UConn

videos.description: Naji Marshall scores 12 consecutive points for Xavier, pulling up for a corner 3 to pump up the crowd in Charleston.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Xavier's Marshall drains crucial 3 in OT) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Xavier's Marshall drains crucial 3 in OT

videos.description: James Bouknight cleans up Tyler Polley's missed 3-pointer with a layup while drawing the foul, leaving just 7.8 seconds on the clock for Xavier and forcing an eventual 2OT.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bouknight sinks key and-1 for UConn) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Bouknight sinks key and-1 for UConn
